des:
Boxing Workout is a fun, realistic, and practical boxing workout program designed by Beyond Boxing, a well-established boxing club in Vancouver, BC, Canada. Our workout is boxing gym-tested and scientifically-proven to improve your fitness level, promote fat loss, increase lean body mass, and much more.
 
To get started, you simply need to say "Open Boxing Workout" and you will be guided through our entire workout program. New exercises, routines, and updates will be regularly added to our Alexa Skill, so please check back often!
